<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 06:09:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列可能会跌倒并再次崛起</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israel-may-fall-and-rise-again/0000018f-89d3-d7f4-adbf-a9ff75c10000</link><description>那些谈论以色列灭亡的人可以分为两类：希望以色列灭亡的人和害怕以色列灭亡的人。以色列人未来可能会失去主权——但这可能不是我们想象的噩梦</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 04:12:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israel-may-fall-and-rise-again/0000018f-89d3-d7f4-adbf-a9ff75c10000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸的 18 个巴勒斯坦牧羊社区最近被消灭。这个可能是下一个</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/18-west-bank-shepherding-communities-have-been-recently-erased-this-one-might-be-next/0000018f-83c5-d9d6-a38f-87ff376b0000</link><description>定居者多年来一直骚扰杰里科附近的一个贝都因小村庄，但在战争期间，他们加大了恐吓力度。身着军服、配备军车的大屠杀分子夺取了该地区的土地，并建立了 13 个新的前哨基地——这一切都是从 10 月份开始的</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 03:50:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/18-west-bank-shepherding-communities-have-been-recently-erased-this-one-might-be-next/0000018f-83c5-d9d6-a38f-87ff376b0000</guid></item><item><title>“犯罪组织正在控制以色列的阿拉伯社会。他们也是为了犹太社会而来”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/crime-orgs-are-controlling-israels-arab-society-theyre-coming-for-jewish-society-too/0000018f-8990-d9d6-a38f-8dfb38780000</link><description>Rawyah Handaqlu 是一个紧急机构的负责人，该机构的成立是为了应对席卷阿拉伯社会的犯罪和暴力浪潮，他谈论了生活在一个犯罪组织取代国家的社会中的感受</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 03:27:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/crime-orgs-are-controlling-israels-arab-society-theyre-coming-for-jewish-society-too/0000018f-8990-d9d6-a38f-8dfb38780000</guid></item><item><title>“我们的鲜血只适合战争”：在加沙作战，他们感到平等。回到以色列的家，这种感觉破碎了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/fighting-in-gaza-they-feel-equal-back-home-in-israel-that-feeling-is-shattered/0000018f-870e-d443-adef-9fce5c9d0000</link><description>在加沙服役和阵亡的以色列士兵中有相当多的埃塞俄比亚人后裔。有些人认为战争已经成为进入以色列社会的一种门票——但代价是什么？</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 02:36:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/fighting-in-gaza-they-feel-equal-back-home-in-israel-that-feeling-is-shattered/0000018f-870e-d443-adef-9fce5c9d0000</guid></item><item><title>第一批人道主义援助物资通过美国新码头抵达加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-live/israeli-air-force-strikes-building-in-west-bank-wanted-terrorist-killed/0000018f-8960-d9d6-a38f-8dfb3ff10000</link><description>以色列国防军发言人：以色列国防军从加沙打捞起三名人质的尸体 ■ 以色列国防军：中士。 20 岁的本·阿维沙伊 (Ben Avishay) 来自纳哈里亚 (Nahariya)，在加沙北部的战斗中身亡。 ■ 哈马斯：美国在加沙地带建造的码头不能替代在巴勒斯坦监督下开放所有陆路过境点 ■ 以色列国防军表示，它杀死了伊斯兰国恐怖组织的武装分子沙哈比勒·赛义德。黎巴嫩 ■ 西班牙首相称马德里只有在与其他国家联合行动时才会承认巴勒斯坦国</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 02:10:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-live/israeli-air-force-strikes-building-in-west-bank-wanted-terrorist-killed/0000018f-8960-d9d6-a38f-8dfb3ff10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列空军袭击约旦河西岸的建筑物；击毙通缉恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-air-force-strikes-building-in-west-bank-kills-wanted-terrorist/0000018f-88b3-d9d6-a38f-8dfb69480000</link><description>据以色列军方称，目标建筑被用作作战作战室</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 22:56:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-air-force-strikes-building-in-west-bank-kills-wanted-terrorist/0000018f-88b3-d9d6-a38f-8dfb69480000</guid></item><item><title>加州大学武装警察与亲巴勒斯坦抗议者发生暴力冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/armed-police-clash-violently-with-pro-palestinian-protesters-at-california-university/0000018f-8898-d9d6-a38f-8dfbee7e0000</link><description>加州大学欧文分校的亲巴勒斯坦营地占领了一座空置建筑，导致警方采取严厉措施，近 50 人被捕</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 22:33:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/armed-police-clash-violently-with-pro-palestinian-protesters-at-california-university/0000018f-8898-d9d6-a38f-8dfbee7e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名在加沙北部战斗中阵亡的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-combat-in-northern-gaza/0000018f-8841-d6b6-a59f-facbb18e0000</link><description>中士。 20 岁的本·阿维沙伊 (Ben Avishay) 来自以色列北部城市纳哈里亚 (Nahariya)，在贾巴利亚 (Jabalya) 与恐怖分子的对抗中身亡。他是自10月7日以来第628名阵亡士兵</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 20:59:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-combat-in-northern-gaza/0000018f-8841-d6b6-a59f-facbb18e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军和辛贝特在加沙地带找到了哈马斯扣押的三名以色列人质的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-retrieves-bodies-of-three-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018f-875c-d7f9-a5ff-b77eecc40000</link><description>沙尼·洛克、阿米特·布斯基拉和伊扎克·格勒伦特都被新星狂欢节劫持为人质。据以色列国防军称，三人从狂欢场跑到梅法西姆交界处，在那里被哈马斯恐怖分子谋杀，尸体被带入加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 16:56:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-retrieves-bodies-of-three-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018f-875c-d7f9-a5ff-b77eecc40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 224 天：大约 75 枚火箭从黎巴嫩向以色列戈兰高地发射</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-224-some-75-rockets-fired-at-israels-golan-heights-from-lebanon/0000018f-8759-d7ca-afcf-97fb75770001</link><description>以色列国防军表示，他们在加沙找到了 10 月 7 日被哈马斯扣为人质的三名以色列人的尸体。 ■ 以色列向国际法院陈述案情。 ■ 中央司令部：第一批运载援助物资的卡车穿过新建的美国码头进入加沙。 ■ 约 75 枚火箭弹从黎巴嫩发射到以色列戈兰高地高地 ■ 以色列极右活动分子袭击了他们以为正在向加沙运送援助物资的阿拉伯裔以色列卡车司机 ■ 战争进入 224 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 16:37:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-224-some-75-rockets-fired-at-israels-golan-heights-from-lebanon/0000018f-8759-d7ca-afcf-97fb75770001</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：向以色列北部发射了 75 枚火箭弹；报告：真主党高级指挥官被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-75-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-report-senior-hezbollah-commander-killed/0000018f-8712-d7ca-afcf-97fb78cc0000</link><description>以色列北部社区的两人受轻伤，一所房屋受损</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 15:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-75-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-report-senior-hezbollah-commander-killed/0000018f-8712-d7ca-afcf-97fb78cc0000</guid></item><item><title>出于想法，内塔尼亚胡将拜登和国防部长加兰特视为密谋反对他的阴谋集团</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/out-of-ideas-netanyahu-sees-biden-and-gallant-as-a-cabal-plotting-against-him/0000018f-8663-d443-adef-9febbcf20000</link><description>加沙战争正在变得像1982年开始的黎巴嫩泥潭一样，带有美国在越南失败的味道。但以色列仍然没有战后计划</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 14:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/out-of-ideas-netanyahu-sees-biden-and-gallant-as-a-cabal-plotting-against-him/0000018f-8663-d443-adef-9febbcf20000</guid></item><item><title>据《华盛顿邮报》报道，以色列军队似乎正在利用加沙医院、学校作为基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/israeli-army-appears-to-be-using-gaza-hospital-school-as-bases-washington-post-reports/0000018f-868c-d443-adef-9fcc60e20000</link><description>卫星图像显示 11 月在土耳其-巴勒斯坦友谊医院周围以及 3 月在 Juhor ad Dik 学校附近修建土堤。上个月，《国土报》发布了卫星图像，显示以色列国防军部队集中在附近的内扎里姆走廊沿线。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 13:43:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/israeli-army-appears-to-be-using-gaza-hospital-school-as-bases-washington-post-reports/0000018f-868c-d443-adef-9fcc60e20000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争是悲惨的，但没有发生种族灭绝：以色列在国际法庭上陈述案情</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/war-in-gaza-tragic-but-no-genocide-taking-place-israel-presents-its-case-at-world-court/0000018f-85ef-d7f9-a5ff-b5ff9a610000</link><description>以色列提出论点，要求国际法院驳回南非停止在拉法行动并从加沙地带撤军的请求。预计下周将就紧急措施请求做出决定</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 11:11:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/war-in-gaza-tragic-but-no-genocide-taking-place-israel-presents-its-case-at-world-court/0000018f-85ef-d7f9-a5ff-b5ff9a610000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在对他来说唯一重要的战争中占据上风：保持权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-the-upper-hand-in-the-only-war-that-matters-to-him-staying-in-power/0000018f-82a7-d7f9-a5ff-b7f725d80000</link><description>任何声称以色列总理没有战略的人都是错误的：他认为政治生存高于一切 ■ 一句随口的话如何概括了以色列处理加沙战争的悲剧 ■ 总理策划了他的“全面胜利”之路到十月</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 03:00:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-the-upper-hand-in-the-only-war-that-matters-to-him-staying-in-power/0000018f-82a7-d7f9-a5ff-b7f725d80000</guid></item><item><title>美国大使：几个月来我们一直在说以色列需要为后哈马斯加沙制定计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-ambassador-weve-been-saying-for-months-israel-needs-a-plan-for-post-hamas-gaza/0000018f-8117-d430-a38f-c5f75aa70000</link><description>大使杰克·卢告诉《国土报》，以色列必须解决战后谁管理加沙的问题。他补充说，以色列在拉法的军事行动迄今为止尚未跨越美国总统乔·拜登划定的底线</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 03:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-ambassador-weve-been-saying-for-months-israel-needs-a-plan-for-post-hamas-gaza/0000018f-8117-d430-a38f-c5f75aa70000</guid></item><item><title>“真正的越南化”：内塔尼亚胡在加沙的战略僵局引发了越来越多的公众异议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-faces-war-on-every-front-but-netanyahu-and-his-arsonist-allies-fan-the-flames/0000018f-82fb-d430-a38f-c7ffc5770000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在宣扬以色列在加沙地带进行军事统治的想法时，追随了本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇的极右路线。 ■ 在以色列国防军，军官们全神贯注于晋升和解雇问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 03:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-faces-war-on-every-front-but-netanyahu-and-his-arsonist-allies-fan-the-flames/0000018f-82fb-d430-a38f-c7ffc5770000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军士兵在加沙北部战斗中丧生；以色列军队在加沙打捞三名人质尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article-live/israelis-attack-troops-who-treated-palestinian-driver-whose-truck-was-torched-by-settlers/0000018f-8436-d7f9-a5ff-b57610bd0000</link><description>以色列要求世界法院驳回南非的停火请愿书 ■ 以色列国防军称，有 75 枚火箭弹向以色列北部发射 ■ 来自黎巴嫩 黎巴嫩报道称，真主党高级指挥官在西顿附近的以色列袭击中丧生 ■ 法国警察击毙了试图袭击以色列的武装男子一座犹太教堂着火 ■ 美国军方表示，第一批援助物资卡车穿过美国码头进入加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 01:52:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article-live/israelis-attack-troops-who-treated-palestinian-driver-whose-truck-was-torched-by-settlers/0000018f-8436-d7f9-a5ff-b57610bd0000</guid></item><item><title>“我认识的每个人现在都在以色列。圣彼得堡已没有一个熟人了。</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-17/ty-article/.highlight/everyone-i-ever-knew-is-now-in-israel-not-one-acquaintance-remained-in-st-petersburg/0000018f-838c-d430-a38f-c7ecd07f0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一位对以色列有责任感的俄罗斯移民，以及分别在以色列、美国和荷兰之间生活的三个兄弟姐妹</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 23:35:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-17/ty-article/.highlight/everyone-i-ever-knew-is-now-in-israel-not-one-acquaintance-remained-in-st-petersburg/0000018f-838c-d430-a38f-c7ecd07f0000</guid></item><item><title>“在哈马斯的囚禁期间，我遇到了一些女孩，她们说：我们将无法应对我们所经历的一切”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-hamas-captivity-i-met-girls-who-said-we-wont-be-able-to-cope-with-what-we-endured/0000018f-830d-d9d6-a38f-87ffe88c0000</link><description>迄今为止，政府新闻办公室拍摄了被释放的以色列俘虏数小时的证词，最终形成了一段 14 分钟的类似公共服务的剪辑。但没有什么可以掩盖前人质所讲述的恐怖</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 22:35:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-hamas-captivity-i-met-girls-who-said-we-wont-be-able-to-cope-with-what-we-endured/0000018f-830d-d9d6-a38f-87ffe88c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>